#DESCRIPTION
# Integrals - FTC - find maximum of f(x) = \int_0^x \{frac(EV2("t^2 - $asquared "),"1+\\cos^2(t)")\} dt
## find the derivative of the function and use it to
## find the local maximum values.
#ENDDESCRIPTION

